## ğŸ¯ Project Objective

The goal of this project is to design and deploy a small but complete RAG system where:

1. Users provide text or documents
2. Content is embedded and stored in a cloud-hosted vector database
3. Relevant chunks are retrieved and reranked
4. A Large Language Model generates a grounded answer
5. All responses include inline citations mapped to source chunks

---

## ğŸ—ï¸ System Architecture

The system follows a Retrieve â†’ Rerank â†’ Generate pipeline to ensure that only the most relevant context is provided to the LLM.

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[User Text / Document Upload] --> B[Chunking: 1000 chars, overlap]
    B --> C[Google text-embedding-004]
    C --> D[(Pinecone Vector Database)]
    
    E[User Query] --> F[Vector Search: Top 10]
    D --> F
    
    F --> G[Cohere Rerank v3.0]
    G --> H[Top 3 Relevant Chunks]
    
    H --> I[Gemini 2.5 Flash]
    I --> J[Final Answer with Inline Citations]
  ## ğŸ“Š Minimal Evaluation (Gold Set)
Tested using the IIT Mandidataset to verify retrieval precision and refusal logic.

| Query | Expected Fact | Result | Citation Correct? |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| "When was IIT Mandi established?" | 2009 | âœ… Pass | âœ… Yes [1] |
| "What are the two main campuses?" | North and South Campus | âœ… Pass | âœ… Yes [1, 2] |
| "Who was the founding director?" | Timothy A. Gonsalves | âœ… Pass | âœ… Yes [1] |
| "What river flows near the campus?" | Uhl River | âœ… Pass | âœ… Yes [2] |
| "Does the campus have a metro station?" | Not mentioned in text | âœ… Pass (Correct Refusal) | N/A |

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack
* Frontend:Streamlit 
* Vector DB:Pinecone (Serverless)
* Embeddings:Google `text-embedding-004`
* Reranker:Cohere `rerank-english-v3.0`
* LLM:Google `gemini-2.5-flash`

